ons. For the POT-enhanced voting, we prove that all vehicles choosing\nto cheat are not a pure Nash equilibrium using game-theoretic analysis.\nSimulation results suggest that the POT-enhanced voting is more robust to\nmalicious data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 11 Apr 2021 18:25:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 20 Dec 2021 05:03:34 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 25 May 2022 17:21:48 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 17 Jan 2023 13:00:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-18"}
