he capability of FAST in RRL measurements, and\na statistically meaningful sample with RRL detection, through which knowledges\nabout Galactic spiral structure and evolution can be obtained, is expected in\nthe future.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 12 Apr 2021 08:08:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 13 Apr 2021 04:15:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-03"}
